name: Metropolitan Museum of Art
description: One of the world's largest and most comprehensive art museums, located on the eastern edge of Central Park.

name: High Line
description: An elevated linear park built on a former New York Central Railroad spur on the west side of Manhattan.

name: 9/11 Memorial
description: A memorial and museum commemorating the September 11, 2001 attacks and the 1993 World Trade Center bombing.
